reviewText: The two controll dvds are amazing. Not as technical as the descriptions led me to believe but still better than most instructionals. However the choke DVD would not play. It said it was formatted for my region but would not play. I was issued a return but don't have a computer and because of my work scedule cant go the the library to print it off. So my three DVD set is a two DVD set. That's the only reason I gave this three stars.
I want to return this item.
